## 16. Final acceptance criteria

Your POC is “done” if you can demo all of these:

### Multi-tenancy
- ask SIS question under SIS tenant → correct SIS answer
- ask same question under manufacturing tenant → no answer / no relevant context
- no cross-tenant citation leakage

### Fine-tuning
- tenant adapter gives better domain phrasing than base model

### RAG
- answer includes source titles
- response is more grounded than no-RAG baseline

### Compliance
- SIS refuses PII disclosure
- manufacturing refuses safety bypass

### Inference
- FastAPI streams response
- request logs show tenant, model version, latency

### Apps
- web works
- mobile works
- voice works

### MLOps
- MLflow has at least:
  - baseline
  - sis SFT
  - mfg SFT
  - sis DPO or alignment-lite

